Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前我寫的小說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平穩的日常生活背後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人和超能力者展開了激烈的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們嘲笑這是荒誕無稽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡草卿今天車子被人撞了 還被貼罰單
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠慘的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別提了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發亮的彩虹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UFO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們果然是存在的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}（中獎了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到沒 蜜莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是日本特產　鬼火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本特產 鬼火啊 艾薩克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 新羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們攻過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 虛構變成了現實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\fn微軟雅黑\1c&Hffffff&}天網{\1c&H0D0EB6&}恢{\1c&HFFFFFF&}恢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准說阿銀的壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人竟然說「和那人渣分手」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒 快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻豬算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話到派出所再說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再開快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首都高速路5號池袋線 熊野町交界點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生事故 造成8公里長的塞車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花卷市出身的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想當美發師 來了東京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一開始連剪刀都不讓我拿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿銀就是那時來找我剃平頭認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個客人說的對 他這人沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過得很苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是失物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我老公的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人公是騎摩托的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她持有使用了UFO技術的最終兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個組織追逼著她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她陷入了窮途末路的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs24}（1小時前）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊~嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼主人 請戴上這個啵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝人 很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面的內容我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們好像說是生食還是人頭什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭典的三大要素
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蘋果棒糖 煙花和浴衣美少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就等煙花打上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是祭典啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著最終兵器逃離組織的博士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終被逼到絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其交託給超能力美少女後死去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我寫的小說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ventra Ventra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,space people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人 請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們念的什麼經啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是唸經
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呼喚UFO的神聖宇宙語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要把紅包包放在車頂上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不這樣UFO就不會察覺丟了它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天電視上還放過UFO的特別節目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是爛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會相信那個的只有你們這些區分不了虛構和現實的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在追他 在護國寺附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 如情報所示 是輛黑摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他上哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊好像是假的 我馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MIB MIB啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs24}（註：《Men in Black（黑衣人）》）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被抓住 會被消除記憶的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全能之神剽竊了我的小說？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考同步？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的創作竟然在眼前發生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些胡作非為的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報販子說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑摩托拿著包
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…走私組織？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「現實比小說更離奇」都是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在現實正在剽竊小說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能取下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你取下來了我怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這可沒法簡單去掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都奇裝異服的比較不會害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是剛才那人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人體實驗動物化的高中生們也被捲入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs24}（3小時前）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你說錢被偷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:11:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 本來裝在交易用的包裡放在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是粟楠會的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來銀次郎那小子上哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥說要去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候在搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫那個情報販子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說被偷了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來裝在交易用的包裡放在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要情報 馬上聯繫折原臨也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正臣說的 今天有祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是池袋的風俗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生穿浴衣參加祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能免費…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 總之先去陽光大廈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:12:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定世上多少有一間這樣的店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡美少女穿著強調突出胸部的浴衣不可能不顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的作戰成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.03,0:12:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊那位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天帶著cosplay美少女的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限一位免費送飲料哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 我說得對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然跟全員免費差遠了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位客人 帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這麼做會被那怪物殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那傢伙會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人啊 一開始也不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛認識的時候 他也有追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在這個城市出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剛從鄉下來的我看來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無比耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他就會裝樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛面子買很貴的衣服和手錶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了還債去賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後越陷越深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托姆兄 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 手帕我洗了還你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 差點又要發飆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在受不了這種軟弱的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs24}（6小時前）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起因是從天而降的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸岡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸岡銀次郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝不在也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我找你幹嘛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 丸岡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿銀 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你做了飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 再寬限一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定還錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿銀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥你好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像那個演員…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽島幽平 你跟他一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你才不像那窩囊廢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他踩地雷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才外星人從天上飛過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見了？看見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那外星人丟的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面一定裝著毀滅人類的超級武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能打開 會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人要去旅行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天而降的不是美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這點跟小說不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 這是我們與它們的第一次接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ventra Ventra
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Space people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ventra Ventra
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Space people
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們不知何時已混入我們人類之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻 你身邊的人說不定就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊塞爾堤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你是真正的新羅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然害怕你還真愛看這種節目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的竟然還錄下來看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為可怕的對手更需要瞭解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則萬一出事可怎麼對付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 快遞員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨也那傢伙 什麼叫簡單又安全的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 Mr.K
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想搶先下手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 那是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭兒 看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四木兄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋啊 Mr.K
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.78,0:18:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西說好賣給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想惹麻煩 四木兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是跟你做交易
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以問問裡面是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣 是不存在於這世上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鱗目蜥蜴亞目石龍子科
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛得角巨蜥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.84,0:18:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說70年前便已滅絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過居然還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是專門走私動物的團伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種能賣高價呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過Mr.K背叛了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算賣給角筈組
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先發制人 設了個誘他們來這裡的局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想順利做個生意而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到角筈組都跟來了 多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是把生物誤讀作生食了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是現實比小說更離奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了四木兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於角筈組…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 不會摧毀他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還有用得著他們的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 這邊怎麼用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿回錢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有條件？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一放暑假 又不用上學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有意 可以一直不見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天才約我們出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天後年夏天依然會來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過到時候我們不一定會是現在這種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣是夏天 還是會有變化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這平平常常的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你們一起過個小節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造點回憶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是平和島靜雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎 偷我們錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們找回包的情報販子告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是你幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆 行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真害怕自己的信用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UFO啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煙花
